{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-3", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "善意背叛", "storyInfo": "自救軍內部因為行動方針展開了爭論，推進之王堅持回到諾伯特區支援格拉斯哥幫的同伴。與此同時，自救軍的所有基地遭到襲擊，情況緊急。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g6_hideout", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#10$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，博士，你們來了。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#10$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，如你們所見，我們的士氣......很低迷。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡亂糟糟的，請別介意。自從阿勒黛......離開後，我們的後勤補給一直是個問題。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，在眼下的麻煩面前，這算是最好解決的一個了。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在上一場戰鬥中，我們的減員很嚴重。我們曾經以為這些犧牲不會白費，只要阻止薩卡茲推進那些工程，一切就還有挽回餘地。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，他們的行動比我們預計的快得多。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲們......他們不僅有碎片大廈，他們還製造了那艘“飛空艇”。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡報已經分發到了大家手上，飛空艇不加掩飾地襲擊了溫德米爾公爵的軍隊，和平的假像已不復存在。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而碎片大廈......薩卡茲既然主動挑起了這場戰爭，那麼，他們對於碎片大廈的掌控......很可能比我們預想的進度還要快。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不敢賭。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......阿勒黛和我提起過這把劍的傳說。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說可以劈開天災的諸王之息是維多利亞最牢固的盾，足以抵擋被牽引而來的風暴。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那她也一定告訴過你，正因為能激發這種力量的人實在罕有，才有了王宮地下“劍座”的存在。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王，你真的沒從這把劍裡感受到什麼嗎？", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是......我不知道，一種召喚？或者微微發熱的感覺？或者是突然能夠運用什麼厲害的源石技藝之類的。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定，你確實可以......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordy", "volume": 0.5, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，什麼都沒有。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這把劍很冷，很硬，揮動起來比錘子要輕一點，不太好掌控力道。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有別的嗎？哪怕只是一點點彆扭的地方——", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......它在上戰場前應該好好地打磨一下，已經有點鈍了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，我們暫時沒辦法指望這把劍能夠直接派上用場，為我們免除碎片大廈的威脅了。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "但它也不會再成為大公爵們互相傾軋的籌碼。;薩卡茲們在啟用碎片大廈前也許會多一些顧慮。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line58", "option2": "line58"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，羅德島的博士，這把劍掌握在我們手中總比在其他勢力手中要好，我們最起碼可以避免它淪為這場戰爭的幫兇，這已經足夠重要。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......足夠重要，是嗎，這已經足夠重要。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）阿勒黛，如果我能......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用灰心，推進之王小姐，也許你只是還沒掌握方法，或者是還不到時候。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那條補給線我已經分析得差不多了，博士。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "起點基本上可以確定是在倫蒂尼姆郊外的布倫特伍德，而終點有很多個。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了海布里區的軍工廠之外，很有可能有一條路線直接延伸到碎片大廈地下。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，我們發現得太晚了，如果早一個月——不，哪怕早十天，事情可能都不會發展到如今的地步。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這條補給線的情報仍然有意義，博士。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這是一條足夠承擔重型物資運輸的線路，並且能夠直通碎片大廈地底——", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那麼，運別的也行。;這是個反攻的機會。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line81", "option2": "line81"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#9$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭爆發後，特雷西斯的身邊很可能沒有太多戍衛，各王庭之主需要指揮自己的部屬對抗各大公爵。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫妖的入局可能會是個問題......但據我對他們的瞭解，他們從不會真正選擇支持誰，更何況，凱爾希女士應該已經與他們的信使談過了。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#7$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願他們聽進去了凱爾希女士的忠告。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#7$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，我們最好——", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，你倒是提一句諾伯特區的事呀！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被那幫薩卡茲混蛋拋出去的可是我們的街區！貝爾德還在那裡！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，比起什麼補給線大反攻，我們得去幫她！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請冷靜一些，我們需要考慮整體局勢......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，騎士閣下想教訓我以大局為重？我可管不了怎麼幹掉一個薩卡茲的老妖怪，現在老子的朋友有危險，老子的家有危險！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想讓我們袖手旁觀？！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我知道你很焦躁，可是我們必須考慮到任何可能的情況。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同樣不建議你們獨自行動，在我們確定那位想搶奪國劍的人徹底放棄計劃之前，你們最好......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最好躲在地下的夾層裡當懦夫？得了吧！我們能應付那些鬼鬼祟祟的傢伙們！現在，最重要的是——", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，因陀羅。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "因陀羅", "content": "我......"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "因陀羅", "content": "好吧。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "針對特雷西斯的行動會在什麼時候開始？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會太快，我們需要偵察那些補給線的具體情況。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎片大廈內部的結構也需要調查。特雷西斯......很強大，任何一點鬆懈都會要了我們的命。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具體時間呢？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半個月內，我希望能在碎片大廈被他真正啟動前......了結這些事。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "足夠了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Dr.{@nickname}，我申請在這次行動之前暫時離隊。請放心，我會在任務開始時回來。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你還是堅持要前往諾伯特區。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我已經失去很多朋友了，克洛維希婭。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有辦法一次又一次地袖手旁觀。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這確實是個出於我個人情感的要求，我不會避諱這一點。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但與此同時，我也認為這是個機會，在我們的正式行動開始之前，解決掉一些潛藏的隱患。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......比如，那些傷害阿勒黛的人，那些想要諸王之息的人。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那無疑是一位大公爵，無論他接下來打算擺出什麼立場，我想......我都該和他好好“談一談”。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸小姐說了，我們的時間並不充裕。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會處理好的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......博士，你怎麼看？", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "......", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line151"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "在那個地塊上，還有件值得注意的事。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line153"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是的，薩卡茲的飛空艇很可能停靠在現在的諾伯特區中。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也意味著......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......特蕾西婭小姐，也許也在那裡。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這場戰爭中，我們一定會面對她，或遲或早。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一件事，Logos先生和我提到過——", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊急......訊......緊急......", "name": "自救軍戰士"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲突襲......卡登區的安全屋......我們......他們的部隊......", "name": "自救軍戰士"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃啊——", "name": "自救軍戰士"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$calamity_intro", "key": "$calamity_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡登區？怎麼回事？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "2", "name": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "offsetx": 300.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧克特里格區的安全屋......", "name": "自救軍戰士"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......襲擊，警報......", "name": "自救軍戰士"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "2", "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "3", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#3$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特！海布里區的安全屋正在遭受襲擊！", "name": "凱瑟琳"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們那邊情況怎麼樣？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#6$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們正在組織還擊，向地下深層撤退，情況很危急，薩卡茲很可能......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}}, {"id": 1